 examples/apparmor/usr.lib.libvirt.virt-aa-helper | 48 ------------------------
 examples/apparmor/usr.libexec.virt-aa-helper     | 48 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 examples/apparmor/usr.sbin.libvirtd              |  4 +-
